  overview_paragraphs = '["The Workforce Management AI Deploy service deploys governed AI capabilities into production with monitoring, safety controls, and operational handover. This AI implementation deploys governed capabilities with monitoring and handover built in.","Put AI-enabled workforce management workflows into production with security, governance, and adoption built in from day one."]'::jsonb,
